# Task: Profile & settings (More page)

## Description

Implement the More/Profile page.

Steps:
1. Replace MorePage placeholder in src/components/pages/MorePage.tsx:

   Layout:
   - Profile section at top:
     - Large avatar (64px)
     - User name (from pageOptions)
     - Email (from pageOptions)
     - 'Edit Profile' link (optional)

   - Storage usage:
     - Progress bar showing used/total space
     - '{used} of {total}' text (bytesToSize)
     - API: seafileAPI.getAccountInfo()

   - Navigation items (grouped sections):
     Section 'Content':
     - Activity (Activity icon → /activity/)
     - My Shares (Share icon → /share-admin/)

     Section 'Settings':
     - Sort Preference (ArrowUpDown icon) → opens SortPreferenceSheet
     - Language (Globe icon) → opens LanguageSheet (or just show current lang)
     - Dark Mode toggle (Moon icon) → toggle dark mode
     - Desktop Version link (Monitor icon) → redirect with ?desktop=1 cookie

     Section 'About':
     - Version info (Info icon): show seafileVersion from config
     - Help (HelpCircle icon): link to docs

   - Logout button (full-width, red text, bottom of page)
     - Calls logout() from api.ts

2. Create src/components/settings/SortPreferenceSheet.tsx:
   - BottomSheet with sort options
   - Default sort: by name or by date
   - Default view: list or grid
   - Persists to localStorage

3. Each navigation item: 44px height, icon left, text center, chevron-right

4. Create tests:
   src/components/pages/__tests__/MorePage.test.tsx:
   - Test renders profile info
   - Test renders navigation items
   - Test logout button calls logout
   - Test storage usage display

Expected result:
- /more/ shows profile, settings, and navigation
- Storage usage bar accurate
- Logout works
- Tests pass

## Files to Modify

- mobile-frontend/src/lib/api.ts
- mobile-frontend/src/lib/config.ts
- mobile-frontend/src/lib/utils.ts

